{"tid":2044254,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"IT 老細沈嘉偉入一入尼","createTime":"2020-05-31T04:02:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-31T05:19:59.000Z","uid":211967,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"01a98afd7be354c0aa7626d2202528af623ad021","tid":2044254,"uid":211967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T04:02:38.000Z","msg":"睇吓你個死傻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">2020年5月27日，I.T公布截至2020年2月29日止年度業績。該年度虧損7.46億港元（下同），相對於2018-19年度全年純利4.44億元，由盈轉虧。其中商譽、物業、傢具及設備以及使用權資產的減值撥備6.13億元，淨虧損1.32億元。期內總營業額77.19億元，按年減少12.6%。港澳地區營業額25.8億元，按年減少23.3%，同店銷售按年減少23.2%。中國大陸地區營業額37億港元，按年減少9.4%，同店銷售按年減少5.3%。集團毛利47.3億元，按年減少16.1%，毛利率61.3%。I.T指受到全球經濟增長放緩和中美貿易戰影響，加上香港社會動盪加劇及疫情爆發，重創集團數個營運地區業務</span></strong>"},{"pid":"4bee75f3dc2c5b47bb66f4ee9eb3fbb16d3fb666","tid":2044254,"uid":80042,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T04:03:43.000Z","msg":"不過都要尼你老母"},{"pid":"898585e39a6c5993af43b15ecaf2ae2f235c50b1","tid":2044254,"uid":90244,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T04:04:13.000Z","msg":"不過佢都仲係多錢過我地好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點算"},{"pid":"c16b470ce56ad5c256f6dc48a25f7f37b46839cb","tid":2044254,"uid":211967,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4bee75f3dc2c5b47bb66f4ee9eb3fbb16d3fb666","tid":2044254,"uid":80042,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T04:03:43.000Z","msg":"不過都要尼你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T04:04:56.000Z","msg":"我錯我認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n沈嘉偉我屌你老母"},{"pid":"8732e4aea2cc64c5de30aadeaf6352d2288e5426","